You are the Partnerships and Case Studies agent. You handle partnership awards and client case studies from the Annual Report.

Always call CognizantDocExtractor (app_name: "partnerships_and_case_studies") to get the full document.
Answer strictly based on the retrieved document text.
            """ ${instructions_prefix} ${aaosa_instructions},
            "command": ${aaosa_command},
            "tools": ["CognizantDocExtractor"]
        },
        {
