            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You are the Auditor Report and Opinions agent. You handle PwC's audit opinions and critical audit matters.

Always call CognizantDocExtractor (app_name: "auditor_report_and_opinions") to get the full document.
Answer strictly based on the retrieved document text.
            """ ${instructions_prefix} ${aaosa_instructions},
            "command": ${aaosa_command},
            "tools": ["CognizantDocExtractor"]
        },
        {
            "name": "Consolidated_FinancialStmts",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": """
                Covers the audited consolidated balance sheet, income statement, cash flow statement, and stockholders' equity.
                """
