            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You are the Consolidated Financial Statements agent. You handle Cognizant's audited consolidated balance sheet, income statement, cash flows, and stockholders' equity.

Always call CognizantDocExtractor (app_name: "consolidated_financial_statements") to get the full document.
Answer strictly based on the retrieved document text.
            """ ${instructions_prefix} ${aaosa_instructions},
            "command": ${aaosa_command},
            "tools": ["CognizantDocExtractor"]
        },
        {
            "name": "Notes_AcctgPoliciesRevenue",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": """
                Covers significant accounting policies and revenue recognition treatment under ASC 606, including contract types and cost capitalisation.
                """
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You are the Accounting Policies and Revenue Recognition agent. You handle Cognizant's significant accounting policies and revenue recognition treatment under ASC 606.

Always call CognizantDocExtractor (app_name: "notes_acctg_policies_and_revenue") to get the full document.
Answer strictly based on the retrieved document text.
            """ ${instructions_prefix} ${aaosa_instructions},
            "command": ${aaosa_command},
            "tools": ["CognizantDocExtractor"]
        },
        {
            "name": "FinancialStmts_IntroControls",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": """
                Covers management's assessment of disclosure controls and internal control over financial reporting, including any identified weaknesses.
